### Implementation 1:
This heuristic prioritizes bins with more remaining space by using the exponential function to scale the remaining space and the item size.

def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return np.exp(bins) * (1 - bins) + np.exp(item)

